vote.title: An ordinance abandoning portions of a drainage easement with a temporary working space easement and a storm sewer easement to MQMF Dallas Carlisle Street LLC, the abutting owner, containing a total of approximately 1,621 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Bowen and Carlisle Streets - Revenue: General Fund $5,400.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee (This item was deferred on August 10, 2022)
